ce and be responsive tothe needs of our customers.  The PIE management team has invested a great dealof time adding increased clarity and focus to our product road map based onmarket feedback.(2)  Make it easy as possible to develop applications and enable solutions forthe Newton platform.  Enhancements to the Newton Toolkit and the availabilityof driver development tools are a top priority.(3)  Do a more effective job in communicating the positioning of Newtonsolutions to individual customers.  We need to strengthen the productpositioning message and deliver on the individual value proposition. The PIE management team is clearly focused on these objectives and is excitedabout the opportunities for the Newton platform in the coming months.^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^o  MARKETING FRONT      NEWTON MARKETING MANAGER DISCUSSES VERTICAL MARKETS              XX        Rebecca Patton, AUSA PIE Marketing Manager, comments on             XX         our marketing front. "After extensive research and            XX          working closely with customers,  we've chosen to focus      XX   XX           on 4 vertical markets in 1995:  HealthCare,        XXX             SalesForceAutomation, Outside Plant and FinancialServices.  These markets represent the largest near-term revenue potential forNewton projects.  Additionally, we believe that forms-based applications willbe a large market with the new forms building tools that make applicationdevelopment faster and easier, like Omniform(tm) (see below), PowerForms (bySestra 402-483-4508) and Tabularasa (by Brand X 800-356-8040).^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^o  VENDOR SPLENDOR      WAYFARER AND OMNIFORM REVIEWED    VV       VV         Wayfarer Communications develops client/server software     VV     VV          that integrates mobile computers into enterprise      VV   VV           networks.  The Wayfarer Enterprise Server NT functions       VV VV            as middleware between enterprise servers and Newton        VVV             MessagePads and Windows notebooks.  It supports theleading forms of wireless and wire-line local and wide-area connectivity media,and supports SQL, SMTP, ODBC and TCP/IP.  A centralized system managementprogram supports enterprise-level administration and security requirements.Custom applications are programmed directly in NTK for Newton and Visual Basicand other languages on Windows.  Applications can integrate SQL databaseaccess, email, alphanumeric paging, triggers and on-line messaging.  For moreinfo contact Wayfarer at (415) 903-1720.^^^^^^^^^^^^OmniForm(tm) is a general purpose data collection system composed of:  1) aMacintosh/Windows-based forms builder package  2)  a Newton-based forms engineand 3)  a Macintosh/Windows-based Data Server.  Forms are designed on theMac/PC and then loaded onto the Newton via modem or serial cable. Forms or surveys can take advantage of a scripting capability that can validatedata, navigate, give alerts, dialogs or using "if-then-else" reasoning promptfor additional questions.   Completed forms give data back to the host where itis easily transferred to databases and spreadsheets. OmniForm allows users to create "intelligent" forms - expanding data collectioncapabilities beyond those of paper forms.  For more info contact WrightStrategies at (800) 666-1228.^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^o  SI ACCESS            PIE DEVELOPER PROGRAMS---EVERYONE NEEDS SUPPORT!       @@               Apple offers three levels Newton developer support:     @@  @@             1)  NEWTON ASSOCIATES PROGRAM:  Access to PIE Developer       @@               Talk discussion board, PIE Developer Info read-only       |                board, developer forums, Newton Developer Mailing, the       |===             Newton Developer CD, discounts on Newton t